cabinet weapons golden~
Almost head high and twice as wide, this cabinet is a tribute to dwarven
craftsmanship. The exterior is gold foil, inlaid with precious stones and 
etched with scenes of battle. The glass front is of such quality it could
only have been created by magic, and the felt-lined interior can hold dozens
of weapons.
~
